replies.body: It looks like you might be having some major packet loss issues, but this might also be somehow related to the patcher loop issues that popped up overnight. Let me know if this is still happening, and if so go ahead and reach out to our tech team in a [**ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new).
